---
import ContentLayout from '../layouts/ContentLayout.astro';
---

<ContentLayout title="Contributing to SANE">
  <p>
    SANE is fully open source. Everything - standards, data, tools, and this website -
    lives in a public GitHub repository. All contributions are welcome.
  </p>

  <h2>Ways to Contribute</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Propose a Standard</strong> - Start with the <a href="/rfc">RFC process</a></li>
    <li><strong>Content</strong> - Glossary terms, blog posts, whitepapers</li>
    <li><strong>Equipment Data</strong> - Add or correct specs in <code>src/data/equipment/</code></li>
    <li><strong>Tools</strong> - Build a calculator in <code>src/pages/tools/</code></li>
    <li><strong>Site</strong> - Fix bugs, improve accessibility, add features</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Getting Started</h2>
  <pre><code>git clone https://github.com/sane-av/sane-av.github.io.git
cd sane-av
npm install
npm run dev</code></pre>

  <p>
    See <a href="https://github.com/sane-av/sane-av.github.io/blob/main/CONTRIBUTING.md">CONTRIBUTING.md</a>
    for the full guide including frontmatter requirements, equipment ID formats,
    commit conventions, and the complete RFC workflow.
  </p>
</ContentLayout>
